Revision history for Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Dpkg

0.05 Apr 10 2013

0.05 Apr 10 2013
  - The file generation code has been modified to pass a pristine copy
    of the template variables every time _generate_file is called.  This
    allows subclasseses overriding or otherwise augmenting _generate_file
    to scribble on the template variables without affecting subsequent
    invocations.

